            <p>
                Basis the Diagnostic Study conducted, LCME prepares a comprehensive report on different aspects of conducting business, clearly identifying the areas of optimum strengths and areas of improvement and shares a proposal with the MSME promoters for working together with them for a duration of minimum one year, extendable by mutual consent with clearly defined objectives. The SMEs/ Consultants of LCME works with the Entrepreneur and their staff  for the Business Transformation, in the areas decided and defined. External audits are conducted to check the progress. The objective of the Consultancy is to transform the Company from a person driven toa Process driven entity.
            </p>
        </div>


        <div class="common-section">
