                <span>Succession Planning Programmes</span>
            </div>
            <p>It’s a common scenario in the Indian MSME landscape that the first generation entrepreneur works  hard to create a company and  run it. However the next generation is somewhat lukewarm to the idea of continuing with the company as an owner. Most first generation owners do not know what and how to do, in a such a scenario. LCME works with the owner to devise and implement the Succession Planning so that the company thrives even after the owners decide to retire or leave the actual running of the business.</p>
        </div>


