                <span>Design Thinking for MSMEs</span>
            </div>
            <p>LCME promotes Design Thinking in the MSMEs which is a user-centric process of finding solutions by observing and empathizing with stakeholders’ needs. Instead of focusing solely on the challenge itself, design thinking considers who is impacted and concentrates on resolving the issues created by the challenge. This is particularly very important for MSMEs as they are producing majorly for the big manufacturers or OEMs.</p>
        </div>



