                <span>Understanding Finances MSME Control</span>
            </div>
            <p>Most MSME owners specially in the manufacturing sector are technically qualified or have learnt the technical aspects. However , Finance is a different ball game altogether, where they face first a mind block and then a road block in arranging finances, preferring to use their own money. The Govt and Banks have different schemes available, but because of lack of awareness, they miss out on it. LCME works with them in this area right from educating to executing support and compliances to make them profitably sustainable.</p>
        </div>



